item.title: The more you know: More IT Girls
item.dc:creator: pacodotio
item.description: Why encourage girls to go into a science, tech, engineering or math career? The U.S. will need more than 1.5 million engineers and computing professionals in the next 10 years. Enough “it girls.” More IT Girls!

item.title: Would you like to play a game?
item.dc:creator: pacodotio
item.description: In this game of high adventure, your objective is to travel 200 miles across the great Gobi Desert while being chased by a tribe of knock-kneed pygmies. High adventure, indeed!
